7
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:56,790
These past years,

8
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:59,030
how have you been?

9
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,240
I've been alright.

10
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,960
I think of you quite often.

11
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:05,790
Back then,

12
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:07,870
I was too young

13
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,950
and blamed you for Mother's death.

14
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:12,150
If not for that,

15
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:14,840
you wouldn't have left for so long.

16
00:01:16,590 --> 00:01:17,680
Everything

17
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,590
is my fault.

18
00:01:20,450 --> 00:01:21,310
I'm so sorry.

19
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:22,150
Jinyang,

20
00:01:23,790 --> 00:01:24,760
actually,

21
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,350
all these years,

22
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,590
I never blamed you.

23
00:01:29,710 --> 00:01:31,950
Then why did you avoid me?

24
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,920
I feared I'd bring you trouble.

25
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:42,200
- Someone poisoned you again?
- Jinyang.

26
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,150
These people are truly heartless.

27
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,510
Even after Mother is gone,

28
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,200
they still refuse to let you go.

29
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,790
You're accused of being born
under a curse

30
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:54,560
based on a reckless claim
by the Astronomical Bureau.

31
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:56,230
It's truly outrageous.

32
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,680
This is the Black Mandrake.

33
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,510
It's proud and hard to tend

34
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,350
with petals shaped like sickles,

35
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:05,760
and the whole plant is poisonous.

36
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:08,240
So, most people avoid raising it.

37
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,400
Yet,

38
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,840
it can save your life.

39
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:19,910
Jinyang, won't you eat?

40
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,280
I've eaten.

41
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,120
I'm not hungry.

42
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,640
Jinyang.

43
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,310
I've grown up now.

44
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,030
From this day forward,

45
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,240
I can protect those I wish to guard.

46
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,890
You've been gone for a long while.

47
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:10,000
Seems I've been played again.

48
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,710
Mind your words.

49
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:13,870
You're siding with outsiders now.

50
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:15,710
Well,

51
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,630
what if we became one family?

52
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,680
Alright, I've troubled you long enough.

53
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,970
I'll take my leave now.

54
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,840
This time,

55
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,840
