56
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,590
No need for thanks between us.

57
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,470
Seeing you make peace with the Princess

58
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,560
brings me great joy as well.

59
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,840
The war begins soon.

60
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,380
