75
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:24,430
Prince Ji led a night assault
on the Xiliang Palace,

76
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,560
killed the King of Xiliang,

77
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,580
and reclaimed the throne.

78
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:28,290
Decades of war between Dayu and Xiliang

79
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:29,430
have finally come to an end.

80
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:31,270
Xiliang has perished.

81
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,150
That's wonderful.

82
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:35,680
What about the Prince?

83
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:36,830
When will he return?

84
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,240
It should be any day now.

85
00:05:38,330 --> 00:05:39,560
