92
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:49,480
The Prince invites you
to the city gate tower.

93
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,630
This way, please.

94
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,070
Go on.

95
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,270
Sure.

96
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:09,750
Your Highness.

97
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,240
