with worries on my mind.

101
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:23,870
How could I not hurry back?

102
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,240
The battle is over now.

103
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,600
What else are you worried about?

104
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:28,710
Well.

105
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,680
It's about your future

106
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:32,680
and happiness.

107
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,200
Chishu.

108
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:42,110
Understood.

109
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:48,590
Your Highness.

110
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,640
