111
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,360
Your betrothal gifts.

112
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,630
Xiyin.

113
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,830
My feelings for you run deep.

114
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,630
